author: Phoebe Hosier
title: Has Tasmania been spared community transmission of coronavirus?
description: Authorities say Tasmania is one of the last remaining jurisdictions in the country not to record any confirmed cases of coronavirus via community transmission. Has the state been spared and will it remain that way?
